Package: bea.gov
Title: Bureau of Economic Analysis (BEA) API Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the BEA API. Access NIPA tables (GDP,
    personal income), GDP by industry, regional economic data, and
    international transactions. Requires a free API key from BEA.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
